@startuml akdb-context
title ArchitecturalKnowledgeDB - System Context
left to right direction
actor "Architecture maintainer" as Maintainer
actor "Coding agent" as Agent
rectangle "ArchitecturalKnowledgeDB" as AKDB
folder "Registered repositories\n(read-only provenance)" as Repos
rectangle "Tiny Tool Observatory\nand other consumers" as Consumers
rectangle "Optional vector backend" as Vector
database "SQLite or PostgreSQL\narchitecture knowledge" as DB
Maintainer --> AKDB : author and query via CLI/API
Agent --> AKDB : author and recall via MCP
Repos --> AKDB : scan/import evidence
AKDB --> DB : canonical DB-native records
AKDB --> Vector : optional semantic recall
AKDB --> Consumers : deterministic SAD/UML export
note bottom of AKDB
SAD/UML created in AKDB use akdb:// source URIs.
Exported files are projections, not authoring inputs.
Imported external evidence retains its source authority.
end note
@enduml
